<h2>FREE ADMISSION!!!<br /> Saturday, March 23<sup>rd</sup> 6-9 pm<br />&nbsp; <br /> Join us at the BYU-Idaho Outdoor Learning Center for a <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>fun family sled night</strong></span>! <br /><br /> We have <span style="text-decoration: underline;">sleds available</span> for your use and no need to walk up the hill, <em>just use the tow-rope</em>! Also, a large canvas tent will be nearby for you and your family to warm up and recharge for another go at the sled hill! <br />&nbsp; <br /> Reserve your spot <a href="https://byui.qualtrics.com/SE/?SID=SV_dg3dW5NdjfgVHfL">here</a>!</h2>
<p><img alt="fun on the sled hill!" height="409" src="Images/badger-creek/Faculty%20Sled%20Night%20Pic.jpg" title="fun on the sled hill!" width="620" /><br /> All families using the sled hill must sign a waiver. You can print the waiver from the link below.<br /> <br /><a href="http://www.byui.edu/Documents/community-connections/Liability%20Waiver.pdf" target="_blank">http://www.byui.edu/Documents/community-connections/Liability%20Waiver.pdf</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p><br /> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Sled Hill Rules</span><br /> 1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; No jumps<br /> 2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; It is the participant's responsibility to avoid other people and objects on the sled hill.<br /> 3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Do not attach a sled rope to the rope tow. Younger participants who can't hold on to the tow rope must be accompanied by an adult.<br /> 4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; All children under the age of 12 must be supervised by an adult.<br /> 5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Each group is responsible to return the sleds to the tow shack.<br /> 6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; All participants must fill out and sign a liability waiver. Participants under 18 must have a waiver signed by their parent or legal guardian.<br /><br /></p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded=""><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Optional" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false" Component="" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/></xPower><xPower Type="Compone